ids":["n27409","n27417"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A8%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"good, wholesome, nice, fine (for example, beneficial, favorable, advantageous; moral, pure, clean; nutritious, nourishing, healthy; tasty, delicious, pleasant, etc.)","examples":[{"text":"كُلُوا مِن طَيِّبَاتِ مَا رَزَقْنَاكُمْ وَلا تَطْغَوْا فِيهِ فَيَحِلَّ عَلَيْكُمْ غَضَبِي وَمَن يَحْلِلْ عَلَيْهِ غَضَبِي فَقَدْ هَوَى","english":"ُO Children of Israel! Eat from the good and wholesome things of what We have allotted to you, and do not transgress with it, so My wrath does not come down upon you. Whomever My wrath comes down upon has lapsed."},{"text":"فمضينا ومعنا من الغناء والآلة والشراب كل شيء ظريف، وأقمنا بالعمر ثلاثة أيام، ومضت لنا به أوقات طيبة،"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"charming, pleasant, agreeable"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"enjoyable"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"tasty, palatable"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَابَ (ṭāba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"goodness, kind-heartedness; agreeability"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fragrance, scent, perfume","examples":[{"text":"لَا طِيبَ يَعْدِلُ تُرْبًا ضَمَّ أَعْظُمَهُ","english":"No perfume equals the dust (earth) which is touching his body."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to season, to spice (food)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make pleasant, to make sweet"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to perfume, to aromatise"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ṭāb- (“good, pleasant”), with levelling to the typical Arabic adjective pattern CayyiC of hollow roots. Cognate with Akkadian 𒁕𒁍𒌝 (ṭābum) and Biblical Hebrew טוֹב (ṭoḇ).\n\nCompare Sabaean 𐩷𐩺𐩨 (ṭyb, “lemongrass”) and Akkadian 𒁵 (ṭabtum, “goodness; salt”)."},"ipa":["/tˤaj.jib/","/tˤiːb/","/tˤaj.ja.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27409","headword_ar":"طِيبٌ","root":"Tyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAba","text_ar":"طَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, Mgh, * Msb, K.) [Used as a simple subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Goodness, pleasantness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bihi mina AlT~iybi","text_ar":"مَا بِهِ مِنَ الطِّيبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in him aught of goodness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: you should not say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn AlT~iybapi","text_ar":"من الطِّيبَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbN","text_ar":"طَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuwbaY","text_ar":"طُوبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Also] a word of well-known meaning; (K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A perfume; a fragrant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an odoriferous, substance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a substance with which one perfumes himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiTor","text_ar":"عِطْر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) [The pl. accord. to Golius and Freytag is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToyaAbN","text_ar":"اَطْيَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawozu AlT~iybi","text_ar":"جَوْزُ الطِّيبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The nutmeg:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwz","text_ar":"جوز"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most excellent"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any sort of thing. (K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToyabu","text_ar":"اَطْيَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibapN","text_ar":"طَيِّبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n27417","headword_ar":"طَيِّبٌ","root":"Tyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbN","text_ar":"طَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, K,) the latter originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ibN","text_ar":"طَايِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and deprived of its medial radical letter, or of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalN","text_ar":"فَعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabiyvN","text_ar":"خَبِيثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in two senses:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant, delightful, delicious, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savoury;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*iy*N","text_ar":"لَذِيذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K; *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"esteemed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant, delightful, delicious, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savoury,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotala*~N","text_ar":"مُسْتَلَذٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in taste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in odour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clean."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEaAmN Tay~ibN","text_ar":"طَعَامٌ طَيِّبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Food"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant in taste;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that descends easily"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and agreeably"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"down the throat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N Tay~ibN","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ طَيِّبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sweet water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pure water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^iHapN Tay~ibapN","text_ar":"رَايِحَةٌ طَيِّبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pleasant, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fragrant, odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibN","text_ar":"طَيِّبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A country that has no salsuginous places in it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a land of good and fertile soil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaEiydN Tay~ibN","text_ar":"صَعِيدٌ طَيِّبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pure ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, Mgh, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkalimu AlT~ay~ibu","text_ar":"الكَلِمُ الطَّيِّبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The good saying"},{"kind":"text","text":"] i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A_il`ha A_il~aA A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"لَا اـِلٰهَ اـِلَّا ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no deity but God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN fiY bayotK Tay~ibK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ فِى بَيْتٍ طَيِّبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is of a good house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"family;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"noble, birth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Tay~ibu AlA_izaAri","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ طَيِّبُ الاـِزَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is continent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chaste."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Tay~ibu AlA^axolaAqi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ طَيِّبُ الاَخْلَاقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant, dispositions;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy in converse, conversable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibu Aln~afosi","text_ar":"طَيِّبُ النَّفْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cheerful, happy, pleased,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dilated, in mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbato nafosuhu","text_ar":"طَابَتْ نَفْسُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosN Tay~ibapN bi$aYo'K","text_ar":"نَفْسٌ طَيِّبَةٌ بِشَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mind cheerful, happy, pleased,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dilated, by means of a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleased, content,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"willing, to grant, concede, give,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"do, a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibapN Eano $aYo'K","text_ar":"طَيِّبَةٌ عَنْ شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleased, willing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"content, to leave, give up, relinquish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be without, a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See, again, 1.)] ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lawful; allowable; allowable by,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agreeable to, law; legitimate; legal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yasotawiY","text_ar":"لَا يَسْتَوِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@loxabiyvu waA@lT~ay~ibu","text_ar":"ا@لْخَبِيثُ وَا@لطَّيِّبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [v. 100], means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The unlawful and the lawful"},{"kind":"text","text":"of property and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the unrighteous and the righteous"},{"kind":"text","text":"of deeds and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sound and the unsound"},{"kind":"text","text":"of tenets or the like and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the good and the bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"of mankind ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall not be equal"},{"kind":"text","text":"in your estimation]. (Mgh.) [See also the next paragraph.]"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}